| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2887 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 56ee86bc-d1c3-5a8b-82dd-fbc2362e6f2a"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
